{"title":"Civilized Cycles Vespa-Modeled eBike has self-leveling suspension, carries passenger","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/24/civilized-cycles-vespa-modeled-ebike-has-self-leveling-suspension-carries-passenger/","date":1624558195000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Civilized Cycles have released an eBike modeled on the Vespa moped, complete with a 750W mid-drive motor, self-leveling suspension and space for a passenger! The Model 1 gets expanding panniers for up to four fully laden shopping bags on a Step-Thru frame for easy mounting and dismounting. Here’s everything we know about the $6,000 US Civilized Cycles Model 1.</p><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/UJPGhdS0F0E?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\" ezoid=\"0.7746268239167713\"></iframe></span></p><h2>Civilized Cycles Model 1</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135435/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-red.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135435/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-red.jpg\" alt=\"civilized cycles model 1 cargo ebike passenger cary\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135435/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-red.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135435/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-red-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135435/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-red-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.ama