s/2021/06/24135435/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-red-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135435/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-red-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>I’ve said it a number of times this year, and I’ll say it again…&nbsp; This has got to be the most well thought-through comprehensive urban eBikes we’ve seen yet (other bikes I’ve said this about include the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/31/specialized-como-sl-powers-up-low-maintenance-urban-ebike-joy-machine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Specialized Como SL</a> and the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/16/the-cannondale-adventure-neo-ebike-promises-comfortable-safe-a-to-b-journeying/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Cannondale Adventure Neo</a>). The technology is progressing at a rate of knots, and the Civilized Cycles Model 1 seems to have it all.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135459/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-two-seater-carry-passenger.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135459/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-two-seater-carry-passenger.jpg\" alt=\"cicilized cycles model 1 ebike carrying passenger\" width=\"1200\" height=\"797\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135459/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-two-seater-carry-passenger.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135459/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-two-seater-carry-passenger-297x197.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135459/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-two-seater-carry-passenger-800x531.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2