ized-cycles-model-1-ebike-single-pivot-rear-suspension-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135956/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-single-pivot-rear-suspension-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135956/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-single-pivot-rear-suspension-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135956/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-single-pivot-rear-suspension-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135956/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-single-pivot-rear-suspension-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135956/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-single-pivot-rear-suspension-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135956/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-single-pivot-rear-suspension-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135956/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-single-pivot-rear-suspension-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a></p><p>The cleverest piece of technology on the Model 1 would have to be the active suspension system which automatically self-adjusts depending on the rider and cargo weight.&nbsp; Underneath the glossy veneer of the fiberglass body is a hydroformed aluminium frame; a front end step-thru piece and a rear swing arm. Civilized Cycles’ images of the early prototypes show a single pivot suspension platform whereby the shock is driven directly by the swingarm.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135411/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carrying-cargo.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimg