r.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135411/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carrying-cargo-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135411/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carrying-cargo-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135411/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carrying-cargo-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135411/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carrying-cargo-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135411/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carrying-cargo-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135411/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carrying-cargo-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135411/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carrying-cargo-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Nothing unusual or technologically advanced there. The interesting thing is that this suspension system self-adjusts, leveling the bike according to the weight it is carrying by adjusting the amount of sag (how deep the bike sits in its travel).</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension.jpg\" alt=\"cicilized cycles model 1 ebike riding\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24140215/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-suspension-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>This means that you can let your much heavier friend borrow the bike, or fill up the expanding panniers with the weekly grocery shop, without having to adjust the suspension to the bike’s new system weight. Civilized Cycles call it their “glide ride” technology, with that suspension designed to soak up any imperfections in the road for a comfortable ride.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135447/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-surmey-archer-5-speed-grip-shift.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135447/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-surmey-archer-5-speed-grip-shift.jpg\" alt=\"cicilized cycles model 1 ebike sturmey archer 5 speed transmission\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135447/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-surmey-archer-5-speed-grip-shift.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135447/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-surmey-archer-5-speed-grip-shift-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135447/cicilized-cycle