https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135447/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-surmey-archer-5-speed-grip-shift-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135447/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-surmey-archer-5-speed-grip-shift-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135447/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-surmey-archer-5-speed-grip-shift-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135447/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-surmey-archer-5-speed-grip-shift-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>The Civilized Cycles Model 1 eBike runs on a 750W mid-drive motor, with a Sturmey Archer 5-Speed Transmission. It can be driven either via pedal-assist, or via the throttle. The changeable battery pack can also be used as a Powerbank for charging devices such as your phone on the go.</p><p>That’s a heap of technology, right? And, there’s more.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135440/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-smart-headlamp.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135440/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-smart-headlamp.jpg\" alt=\"cicilized cycles model 1 ebike headlamp\" width=\"1200\" height=\"824\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135440/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-smart-headlamp.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135440/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-smart-headlamp-297x204.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135440/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-smart-headlamp-800x5