or.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135423/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-integrated-tailight-braking-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135423/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-integrated-tailight-braking-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135423/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-integrated-tailight-braking-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135423/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-integrated-tailight-braking-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135423/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-integrated-tailight-braking-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135423/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-integrated-tailight-braking-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Security is taken into account, too. It can be locked by PIN via its onboard display or remote app and it features GPS theft tracking.</p><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Uh9Ac7y8bDU?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></span></p><p>As far as we can tell, the bike will be available in one size only. The handlebar features a dramatic backsweep, bringing the cockpit close to the rider for ease of control. We don’t have a geometry chart for the bike yet, but the marketers tell us the seat can be set low enough for most riders to plant their feet on the ground firmly to allow a passenger to mount the bike.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135405/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carries-passenger.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135405/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carries-passenger.jpg\" alt=\"cicilized cycles model 1 ebike passenger onboard\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135405/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carries-passenger.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135405/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carries-passenger-297x297.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135405/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carries-passenger-800x800.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135405/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carries-passenger-120x120.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135405/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carries-passenger-768x768.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135405/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carries-passenger-696x696.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135405/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carries-passenger-1068x1068.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135405/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carries-passenger-420x420.jpg 420w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/24135405/cicilized-cycles-model-1-ebike-carries-passenger.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazo